Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I time leaped, over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if Moeka and SERN never attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was like fate itself kept murdering her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like the entire world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,475)\i1}was conspiring to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cars aren't moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a back road or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really an option, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mayushii's watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.69,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Okabe Rintarou has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.93,0:01:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter what I try,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Organization... Steins Gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no such thing!
