Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got to the individual character route.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me save{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's after Mayuri's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how many times I try to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the end...
